<i>from the very beginning...</i>

00:29.905 --> 00:34.284
<i>it was the children
who gave me my power.</i>

00:34.368 --> 00:37.246
<i>The Springwood Slasher...</i>

00:37.246 --> 00:39.164
<i>that's what they called me.</i>

01:02.187 --> 01:05.440
<i>My reign of terror
was legendary.</i>

01:05.566 --> 01:09.570
<i>Dozens of children
would fall by my blades.</i>

01:12.823 --> 01:16.660
<i>Then the parents of Springwood
came for me...</i>

01:22.124 --> 01:26.253
<i>taking justice
into their own hands.</i>

01:28.255 --> 01:32.259
<i>When I was alive, I might
have been a little naughty...</i>

01:32.259 --> 01:34.011
<i>but after they killed me,</i>

01:34.052 --> 01:37.347
<i>I became something much,
much worse--</i>

01:37.347 --> 01:40.392
<i>the stuff nightmares
are made of.</i>

01:41.518 --> 01:42.853
<i>The children
still feared me...</i>

01:42.978 --> 01:46.857
<i>and their fear gave me the power
to invade their dreams.</i>

01:46.940 --> 01:51.111
<i>And that's when the fun
really began!</i>

01:54.323 --> 01:59.494
<i>Until they figured out
a way to forget about me...</i>

01:59.494 --> 02:02.456
<i>to erase me completely!</i>

02:02.456 --> 02:04.208
<i>Being dead wasn't a problem.</i>

02:04.208 --> 02:07.294
<i>But being forgotten--
now, that's a bitch!</i>

02:11.048 --> 02:12.341
It's only a dream!

02:12.466 --> 02:13.800
Die, motherfucker!

02:13.842 --> 02:17.012
<i>I can't come back
if nobody remembers me!</i>

02:17.012 --> 02:21.141
<i>I can't come back
if nobody's afraid!</i>

02:25.145 --> 02:28.774
<i>I had to search the bowels of hell...</i>

02:28.774 --> 02:31.568
<i>but I found someone...</i>

02:31.568 --> 02:35.197
<i>someone who'll make 'em remember.</i>

02:35.197 --> 02:39.701
<i>He may get the blood,
but I'll get the glory.</i>

02:39.701 --> 02:43.997
<i>And that fear is my ticket home.</i>

02:45.374 --> 02:46.416
Mike?

02:48.669 --> 02:50.045
Is that you?

02:54.174 --> 02:55.425
All right, fuck you, then.

02:55.509 --> 02:56.468
I'm heading in.

03:11.149 --> 03:12.734
Mike?

03:12.776 --> 03:14.736
Come on, it's not funny anymore.

04:43.033 --> 04:43.992
No!

04:47.871 --> 04:49.164
<i>Jason.</i>

04:54.670 --> 04:58.423
<i>I should've been watching
them, not drinking...</i>

04:58.423 --> 05:00.384
<i>not meeting a boy
at the lake.</i>

05:01.969 --> 05:03.971
<i>I deserve to be punished.</i>

05:04.012 --> 05:06.431
<i>We all deserved
to be punished.</i>

05:06.431 --> 05:08.976
<i>Jason.</i>

05:10.394 --> 05:12.938
My special, special boy.

05:12.980 --> 05:16.191
Do you know what
your gift is?

05:16.275 --> 05:17.734
No matter what they do to you...

05:17.776 --> 05:19.862
