05:19.862 --> 05:22.281
You can never die.

05:23.740 --> 05:25.617
You've just been
sleeping, honey.

05:25.659 --> 05:30.581
But now the time
has come to wake up.

05:31.665 --> 05:34.585
Mommy has something
she wants you to do.

05:35.669 --> 05:38.714
<i>I need you to go
to Elm Street.</i>

05:38.714 --> 05:43.260
<i>The children have been
very bad on Elm Street.</i>

05:43.260 --> 05:45.846
<i>Rise up, Jason!</i>

05:45.846 --> 05:49.016
<i>Your work isn't finished!</i>

05:49.016 --> 05:52.769
<i>Hear my voice and live again!</i>

06:02.237 --> 06:05.574
Make them remember me, Jason.

06:05.574 --> 06:08.535
