the convent, Lori.

09:04.127 --> 09:05.796
You need to meet a guy.

09:22.980 --> 09:25.107
Hey, Lori...

09:25.148 --> 09:28.277
I like the...
flow of your place.

09:28.277 --> 09:30.195
Got good feng shui.

09:30.195 --> 09:32.030
Yeah.

09:39.288 --> 09:41.707
You know about feng shui?

09:41.707 --> 09:43.041
Oh, oh!

09:43.041 --> 09:44.042
Oh, you should see her bedroom!

09:44.042 --> 09:46.753
-Hmm?
-Great flow in there.

09:46.795 --> 09:49.381
Lori, why don't you go upstairs
and show Blake your feng shui?

09:49.381 --> 09:50.632
Shut up!

09:52.885 --> 09:54.511
I got a kink in my neck.

09:54.511 --> 09:58.015
Come on.
You can massage it out for me.

09:59.850 --> 10:01.310
I think I need
a few more drinks...

10:01.310 --> 10:03.437
before there'll be
any massaging.

10:04.688 --> 10:06.315
What do you see in him?

10:06.398 --> 10:09.193
I don't know,
but he has a cute ass.

10:09.193 --> 10:12.487
Babe, don't make me
ask you twice, OK?

10:18.035 --> 10:19.745
So, Lori...

10:19.745 --> 10:21.663
am I gonna get that
grand tour or what?

10:21.747 --> 10:23.916
Yeah.

10:23.999 --> 10:25.501
You know, why don't you
start in the kitchen...

10:25.501 --> 10:26.585
and get us some beers?

10:26.585 --> 10:28.003
Cool.

10:31.882 --> 10:34.134
Oh, my God, Kia,
he is a total idiot.

10:34.134 --> 10:35.093
Get him out of here.

10:35.093 --> 10:37.346
Oh, Lori, come on,
give him a chance.

10:37.346 --> 10:38.472
I don't like him.

10:38.555 --> 10:40.349
You know what?
You don't like anybody.

10:40.474 --> 10:42.059
I mean, Lori, you've
barely gone out since--

10:42.142 --> 10:44.144
Since what?
Since my mom died?

10:44.186 --> 10:45.812
Yeah, well, you know what?
My dad needs me.

10:45.896 --> 10:47.689
So I can't just go out
with guys all the time...

10:47.814 --> 10:50.984
and if I did, it would not be
with somebody like Blake.

11:30.274 --> 11:31.859
Yeah, fuck me, baby!

11:45.747 --> 11:48.041
Your back door was open.

11:48.167 --> 11:49.209
I closed it.

11:49.251 --> 11:50.544
Mmm.

11:50.627 --> 11:54.840
Babe, you know I don't like
to be touched after, OK?

11:54.965 --> 11:57.509
Fine. I'll go have
a shower then.

11:59.344 --> 12:01.555
Good.

12:01.680 --> 12:03.891
Your hair smells like
menthols, anyway.

12:03.891 --> 12:05.559
Asshole.

12:59.613 --> 13:01.865
Trey!

13:01.907 --> 13:04.660
What the hell are you doing?

13:23.136 --> 13:24.555
Help us! Help us!

13:24.638 --> 13:27.266
Oh, my God!

13:27.266 --> 13:29.434
Over here!

13:29.434 --> 13:31.270
Please help us!

13:31.270 --> 13:32.229
Help us!

13:32.229 --> 13:33.522
You kids need
some assistance?

13:33.564 --> 13:35.566
What the fuck
do you think?!

13:35.649 --> 13:37.401
We need to lock this down now.

13:37.484 --> 13:38.902
Keep it contained, you hear me?

13:38.902 --> 13:40.487
Killed in bed.

13:40.529 --> 13:43.073
Jesus.

13:43.073 --> 13:45.450
It's even the same damn house.

13:45.450 --> 13:46.910
1428 Elm.

13:46.910 --> 13:48.787
It's gotta be him, right?

13:48.787 --> 13:50.289
It's gotta be
Freddy Krueger.

13:50.372 --> 13:51.206
Hey! Don't even say...

13:51.331 --> 13:52.207
that son of a bitch's
name out loud.

13:52.249 --> 13:54.251
Let's just keep it together.

13:54.376 --> 13:56.753
We've been through too much
to let this thing spread now.

13:56.837 --> 13:58.172
Take all the kids
down to the station.

13:58.255 --> 13:59.715
Keep them separate.
Do it now.

13:59.715 --> 14:01.049
Yes, sir.

14:01.175 --> 14:02.384
We'll be in touch.

14:02.384 --> 14:04.261
Thank you.
Let's go home.

14:07.931 --> 14:10.267
So?

14:10.267 --> 14:11.476
She doesn't know anything.

14:11.476 --> 14:13.854
None of them do.

14:13.854 --> 14:14.980
I'm pretty sure we're good.

14:14.980 --> 14:16.982
Pretty sure?
You better make damn sure...

14:16.982 --> 14:18.066
none of those kids
knows anything...

14:18.192 --> 14:20.402
or I'll send your ass up
to Westin Hills with them.

14:20.485 --> 14:21.778
Knows what?
What do you mean?

14:21.862 --> 14:23.655
Good work there tonight, Stubbs.

14:23.655 --> 14:25.657
Right place, right time.

14:25.782 --> 14:27.618
But we'll take it
from here, all right?

14:35.834 --> 14:37.127
Your father's on his way.

14:37.169 --> 14:38.337
Do they know who did this?

14:38.337 --> 14:40.339
No, not yet.

14:40.339 --> 14:41.423
But I thought I heard...

14:41.423 --> 14:43.133
one of the officers
mention a name.

14:43.133 --> 14:44.635
You know, to tell
you the truth, Lori...

14:44.718 --> 14:46.762
I--I just moved here
about a month ago...

14:46.762 --> 14:49.139
but if they have a suspect,
I'd be the first to know.

14:49.181 --> 14:50.891
But they asked me all these
really weird questions...

14:50.891 --> 14:52.142
Iike about my dreams--

15:01.443 --> 15:03.028
What was the name?

15:04.613 --> 15:06.532
What was the name?

15:11.495 --> 15:13.080
Freddy.

15:30.848 --> 15:32.516
Hello?

16:22.232 --> 16:24.151
Are you OK?

16:27.988 --> 16:30.699
His name is Freddy Krueger...

16:30.782 --> 16:36.288
and he loves children,
especially little girls.

16:36.371 --> 16:38.832
Freddy's coming back.

16:38.832 --> 16:41.376
Soon he'll be strong enough.

16:41.376 --> 16:44.588
It's OK to be afraid.

16:44.671 --> 16:46.590
We were all afraid.

16:46.673 --> 16:50.052
Warn your friends.
Warn everyone.

16:59.478 --> 17:03.774
<i>One, two, Freddy's
coming for you</i>

17:03.899 --> 17:07.444
<i>Three, four,
better lock the door</i>

17:07.444 --> 17:11.656
<i>Five, six, grab a crucifix</i>

17:11.698 --> 17:15.368
<i>Seven, eight,
try to stay up late</i>

17:15.368 --> 17:19.289
<i>Nine, ten, never sleep again</i>

17:19.373 --> 17:23.669
<i>One, two, Freddy's
coming for you...</i>

17:30.551 --> 17:33.929
Blake, we have to talk.

17:38.100 --> 17:39.977
What the hell were you
doing over there?

17:39.977 --> 17:42.271
You were supposed to be
watching your sister.

17:42.271 --> 17:44.773
Were you drinking?

17:44.773 --> 17:47.651
My best friend was
just killed, Dad!

17:47.651 --> 17:51.196
So how about giving me
some fucking space?

17:52.948 --> 17:54.992
You watch yourself, boy.

18:06.920 --> 18:09.756
I'm gonna get him for you, Trey.

18:09.756 --> 18:11.925
Cop let it slip.

18:11.925 --> 18:13.510
It was somebody named Freddy.

18:13.552 --> 18:16.471
I'm gonna take him out
myself, Trey.

18:16.471 --> 18:19.683
I swear to God.

18:33.822 --> 18:35.574
Who is that?

18:35.574 --> 18:38.243
Someone there?

18:47.211 --> 18:48.337
Jesus.

18:56.803 --> 18:59.348
I'm OK. I'm all right.

19:03.602 --> 19:05.854
Not strong enough yet.

19:05.854 --> 19:09.191
Well, I will be soon enough.

19:09.191 --> 19:12.402
Until then...

19:12.402 --> 19:15.489
I'll let Jason have some fun.

19:24.289 --> 19:25.499
Dad?

19:49.690 --> 19:53.151
Hypnocil.
What does this shit do, anyway?

19:53.151 --> 19:54.736
How come we all
have to take it?

19:54.736 --> 19:58.365
It keeps you nice and docile
while I kick your little ass.

20:01.201 --> 20:03.203
I'm fine with that.

20:04.955 --> 20:08.542
<i>We interrupt this program
for a special report.</i>

20:08.542 --> 20:09.543
<i>After tonight's murder...</i>

20:09.543 --> 20:11.295
<i>in this neighborhood
of Springwood...</i>

20:11.295 --> 20:12.921
<i>the Sheriff's Department
has confirmed...</i>

20:12.963 --> 20:14.882
<i>that there is one victim...</i>

20:14.965 --> 20:16.091
Hey, turn that up, man.

20:16.133 --> 20:18.135
Remain sketchy,
but the sheriff--

20:18.260 --> 20:20.554
Sorry, Will.
You know the rules.

20:20.637 --> 20:21.597
Turn that back on.

20:21.722 --> 20:23.849
I know somebody
that lives in that house.

20:23.891 --> 20:25.642
Come on, turn it back on, man!

20:25.642 --> 20:26.935
I never ask for anything.

20:26.935 --> 20:29.438
Just turn on
the fucking TV, please!

20:32.941 --> 20:33.817
Fuck you, man!

20:33.901 --> 20:35.903
What the fuck is your problem?

20:35.986 --> 20:37.112
What are you doing, man?

20:37.112 --> 20:39.364
You want 10ccs of that pink
tranquilizer in your ass?

20:39.406 --> 20:40.949
That was Lori's house.

20:40.949 --> 20:42.868
They said something
about a murder.

20:42.868 --> 20:43.911
I gotta go to her.

20:43.911 --> 20:45.496
I gotta see if she's OK.

20:45.496 --> 20:47.498
Back to Springwood?

20:47.539 --> 20:49.750
