dream demon shit again.

20:51.752 --> 20:55.172
OK? You know that's all
just in your head.

20:55.255 --> 20:58.467
Yeah, yeah, and who are you,
the poster boy for sanity?

20:58.509 --> 20:59.510
You're the one
that told the cops...

20:59.510 --> 21:01.011
