21:01.094 --> 21:02.513
Yeah, right, and now it
looks like someone else...

21:02.596 --> 21:03.639
got killed in the same house.

21:03.639 --> 21:05.140
You think that's
a coincidence?

21:05.265 --> 21:07.643
Two murders in one house?

21:07.643 --> 21:10.896
Kurt, how many times
do I have to tell you, man?

21:11.021 --> 21:12.606
I don't do checkers.

21:12.606 --> 21:14.525
I'm an UNO guy, all right?

21:14.525 --> 21:18.362
So go grab the fucking UNO deck
and we'll play, OK?

21:18.362 --> 21:19.696
Please. Thank you.

21:22.199 --> 21:25.160
Look at us, Will.

21:25.202 --> 21:27.162
Look around you, man.

21:27.204 --> 21:29.164
We're institutionalized.

21:30.541 --> 21:33.627
