We're not going anywhere.

21:42.261 --> 21:44.263
I do miss my family, man.

21:44.263 --> 21:50.018
I mean, it's been four years
since I've seen 'em, you know.

21:50.018 --> 21:51.895
All these years,
and you're still convinced...

21:51.895 --> 21:53.230
you saw her father do that?

21:53.272 --> 21:55.023
I know what I saw, Mark.

21:55.023 --> 21:58.026
Fuck what the doctors try
to get me to believe.

21:58.068 --> 21:59.903
I need to know if she's OK.

22:16.044 --> 22:17.171
You want to play?

22:31.393 --> 22:33.812
Sweet dreams, monkey boy.

22:37.024 --> 22:38.650
What the hell
was that for, man?

22:40.652 --> 22:42.362
Heh heh heh!

22:45.699 --> 22:47.951
You're a fucking lunatic,
you know that?

22:48.035 --> 22:50.412
I know you are,
but what am l?

23:06.428 --> 23:07.930
Are you sure
you didn't see anyone?

23:08.013 --> 23:10.849
No, Dad, none of us did.

23:10.974 --> 23:13.769
