23:27.157 --> 23:29.785
Dad, I'm not going anywhere.

23:31.370 --> 23:33.288
I promise.

23:33.288 --> 23:35.499
Look at you.

23:35.499 --> 23:36.750
You're exhausted.

23:36.750 --> 23:39.336
Lori.

23:39.419 --> 23:41.505
