23:44.132 --> 23:46.134
I don't want to
go to sleep, Dad.

23:46.134 --> 23:47.678
I just want to see my friends.

23:47.678 --> 23:50.389
I don't think it's a good idea
for you to go to school today.

23:50.389 --> 23:52.349
You've just been through
a very traumatic experience.

23:52.349 --> 23:54.601
Dad, please...

23:54.601 --> 23:57.020
I just need to get
out of the house, OK?

23:57.062 --> 24:00.274
I'll be fine.
I promise.

24:07.239 --> 24:09.074
Well, at least drink your juice.

24:14.288 --> 24:15.622
Will Rollins
and the Davis boy...

24:15.706 --> 24:17.457
escaped from Westin Hills
last night.

24:17.541 --> 24:19.710
Oh, Jesus.

24:19.710 --> 24:21.879
It's all coming apart again.

24:21.920 --> 24:24.423
Don't worry.
We'll find them.

24:24.464 --> 24:26.466
Keep this thing contained.

24:38.187 --> 24:39.354
Lori!

24:39.438 --> 24:42.608
Oh, my God! God, you guys,
I'm so glad you're here.

24:42.608 --> 24:44.359
Blake's dead, too.

24:44.484 --> 24:46.486
What?

24:46.486 --> 24:48.739
Yeah, he--

24:50.324 --> 24:54.119
He was stabbed
to death late last night.

24:54.119 --> 24:56.205
Same with his dad.

24:56.330 --> 24:57.956
What?

24:59.917 --> 25:02.794
Shit, shit!
This is bullshit!

25:02.794 --> 25:04.213
The police are blaming
everything on Blake...

25:04.296 --> 25:06.215
Iike its some kind
of Columbine thing or something.

25:06.256 --> 25:07.966
They're saying he went crazy.

25:07.966 --> 25:10.886
Killed Trey, killed his dad,
and then took his own life?

25:10.928 --> 25:13.096
This is so fucking messed up.

25:13.096 --> 25:14.640
This is messed up.

25:15.891 --> 25:17.309
Excuse me. Sorry.

25:17.309 --> 25:18.769
Lori?

25:18.769 --> 25:20.229
What is it, Linderman?

25:20.270 --> 25:21.647
Um, well, I heard
what happened,

25:21.647 --> 25:23.482
and I just wanted to
express how, um...

25:23.565 --> 25:26.026
well, to tell you
how sorry I was.

25:26.026 --> 25:28.195
Thank you.
That's sweet.

25:28.278 --> 25:30.989
Right. Actually if you need
anybody to talk to or maybe--

25:31.073 --> 25:33.158
Whoa, Linderman,
let me give you a tip.

25:33.158 --> 25:35.077
Place your hormones
back in the box...

25:35.077 --> 25:36.578
and quit while
you're ahead, OK?

25:36.662 --> 25:38.413
We don't have time
for Date-a-Dork right now.

25:38.413 --> 25:39.540
Thanks.

25:40.749 --> 25:42.417
Right. Sorry.

25:42.417 --> 25:44.336
I swear, every day
it's the same thing.

25:44.336 --> 25:45.879
He's like one of those
fucking froufrou dogs...

25:45.879 --> 25:47.214
that keeps humping your leg.

25:48.882 --> 25:50.259
Give a couple to some ladies.

25:50.342 --> 25:51.510
Thanks, man.

25:51.510 --> 25:52.469
I see what
you're saying, Gibb...

25:52.469 --> 25:53.512
but that's exactly
why you should go.

25:53.512 --> 25:55.222
I mean, be amongst friends,
where it's safe.

25:55.222 --> 25:56.473
There's gonna be a whole lot
of loving there for you...

25:56.473 --> 25:58.600
and my boy Trey, all right?

25:58.642 --> 26:00.227
Yeah. Yeah, you're right.
I should go.

26:00.310 --> 26:02.020
I could use a few dozen drinks.

26:02.020 --> 26:02.980
That a girl.

26:02.980 --> 26:04.731
Let your freak flag fly.

26:04.773 --> 26:06.316
See you there.

26:06.400 --> 26:07.276
You want to go?

26:07.401 --> 26:09.194
No, I don't think so.

26:09.194 --> 26:11.530
I--I didn't get much
sleep last night...

26:11.572 --> 26:13.031
and when I did sleep...

26:13.031 --> 26:14.616
I had the most
terrible nightmares.

26:14.616 --> 26:16.743
Lori, you had to sleep
at a police station.

26:16.743 --> 26:18.078
I'd have nightmares, too.

26:18.078 --> 26:19.538
No, no, no,
it wasn't like that.

26:19.580 --> 26:21.415
I mean, this was really real.

26:21.415 --> 26:23.041
I mean, there was this man...

26:23.041 --> 26:25.043
but he more like
a monster really...

26:25.043 --> 26:26.378
and they kept
calling him Freddy...

26:26.378 --> 26:28.130
-and he was so real.
-Shh!

26:28.130 --> 26:29.423
What did he look like?

26:29.464 --> 26:32.217
He--he had this...

26:32.217 --> 26:33.969
dark brown hat, and...

26:33.969 --> 26:36.263
his skin was
terribly burnt...

26:36.388 --> 26:38.640
and on this right hand
he had this like these...

26:38.682 --> 26:40.017
razor fingers, and--

26:40.142 --> 26:41.351
You must be tripping.

26:41.435 --> 26:42.519
No, no, no!

26:42.519 --> 26:43.896
And then there were
these little girls...

26:43.896 --> 26:45.647
It's OK.
It was a bad dream.

26:45.731 --> 26:47.983
They were singing like
this--this song like--

26:47.983 --> 26:52.821
One, two, Freddy's
coming for you.

26:52.946 --> 26:54.948
You know why they sing that?

26:54.990 --> 26:57.367
Because that's when
he comes for you...

26:57.493 --> 26:59.328
in your dreams.

26:59.369 --> 27:01.371
You're lucky to be alive.

27:01.497 --> 27:02.706
Who is he?

27:02.706 --> 27:04.166
He's a child murderer...

27:04.291 --> 27:06.168
that some parents
from around here burned alive...

27:06.168 --> 27:08.420
but then he came back.

27:08.420 --> 27:11.632
Back for revenge
in our nightmares.

27:11.673 --> 27:13.217
Funny no one ever
told us about him, huh?

27:13.300 --> 27:14.468
-OK, thank you!
-No!

27:14.468 --> 27:15.552
You want some free advice?

27:15.636 --> 27:17.387
Coffee.
Make friends with it.

27:17.387 --> 27:18.889
Mark!

27:18.972 --> 27:20.098
That's enough.

27:21.517 --> 27:23.018
You're scaring her.

27:26.897 --> 27:28.982
Will?

27:28.982 --> 27:31.151
Hey.

27:34.530 --> 27:37.449
I thought you might
be in trouble, so we--

27:37.449 --> 27:38.909
Lori! Oh, my God!

27:38.909 --> 27:39.993
Lori, honey, wake up!

27:40.077 --> 27:42.371
Someone get help, please!

27:42.496 --> 27:43.872
Someone get some help, please!

27:43.997 --> 27:47.835
The principal!
Will, let's go, let's go!

27:47.876 --> 27:49.586
Please, somebody help her.
Lori?

27:57.636 --> 27:59.972
How much longer
is it gonna take?

27:59.972 --> 28:01.598
-ls she OK or what?
-Shh!

28:01.598 --> 28:03.350
Tsk!

28:25.622 --> 28:28.333
For nose jobs,
what kind of anesthesia...

28:28.333 --> 28:29.960
do the doctors use?

28:29.960 --> 28:31.545
They put you
all the way under, right?

28:45.809 --> 28:46.977
Got your nose!

28:53.859 --> 28:55.360
Strong work, man.

28:55.360 --> 28:56.486
I came to make sure she's OK...

28:56.486 --> 28:58.739
and you put her
in the infirmary.

29:02.242 --> 29:03.702
What were you
thinking about...

29:03.702 --> 29:05.454
telling her
all that stuff, man?

29:05.454 --> 29:06.663
I mean, we're not in group.

29:06.663 --> 29:07.748
Because I'm thinking
for the first time in my life...

29:07.748 --> 29:09.583
that maybe I'm not crazy...

29:09.583 --> 29:11.084
that my brother wasn't crazy.

29:11.084 --> 29:13.045
She had the same dream, Will.

29:13.045 --> 29:14.963
Will Rollins!
Mark Davis!

29:24.932 --> 29:26.308
This doesn't make any sense.

29:26.308 --> 29:27.643
There's nothing on Krueger.

29:27.768 --> 29:30.604
Not his arrest, his death,
not even a birth certificate.

29:30.687 --> 29:33.232
Whole sections of
the records are gone.

29:33.232 --> 29:36.443
Look at all these
blacked-out obituaries.

29:44.117 --> 29:45.702
January eighteenth.

29:45.786 --> 29:48.914
That's the day my brother
committed suicide.

29:48.997 --> 29:50.916
Why isn't that in here?

29:52.835 --> 29:55.462
I don't know!

29:55.462 --> 29:57.714
But I'm sure there's
a good reason.

29:59.132 --> 30:00.592
Remember in group
when they told us...

30:00.592 --> 30:01.969
not to jump to conclusions?

30:01.969 --> 30:03.053
Listen to yourself.

30:03.053 --> 30:04.888
You're holding onto
that psychobabble bullshit...

30:04.888 --> 30:07.391
Iike it's some kind of
security blanket, man.

30:07.391 --> 30:10.894
Let it go.
They've covered him up, Will.

30:10.894 --> 30:12.271
They never told us
about Freddy...

30:12.271 --> 30:14.147
because that's how they
decided to beat him.

30:14.147 --> 30:16.942
They treated him like he
was a fucking disease...

30:16.942 --> 30:17.985
and they locked up
all the kids...

30:17.985 --> 30:18.944
who had made
contact with him...

30:18.944 --> 30:20.571
so they wouldn't
infect the others.

30:20.654 --> 30:21.864
That's crazy.

30:21.864 --> 30:24.241
Is it?

30:24.241 --> 30:26.410
How come we were
never allowed...

30:26.493 --> 30:28.912
to call any of
our friends, man?

30:28.912 --> 30:31.123
How come none of our
friends ever called us?

30:31.206 --> 30:34.042
We were in a fucking
quarantine, man.

30:34.168 --> 30:36.545
That's what
Westin Hills was for.

30:36.545 --> 30:38.797
Well, even if all
you're saying is true...

30:38.797 --> 30:41.091
then why didn't
Freddy kill Lori?

30:41.216 --> 30:43.594
Maybe he's not
strong enough yet.

30:43.635 --> 30:46.138
My brother said it's our fear
that gives him his power.

30:46.221 --> 30:47.514
Yeah, well,
you sure as hell...

30:47.514 --> 30:50.017
spread enough fear
today at school.

30:50.017 --> 30:51.894
Holy shit.

30:56.064 --> 30:57.274
You're right.

30:57.357 --> 31:01.361
They wanted to forget Freddy so
they wouldn't fear him.

31:01.361 --> 31:03.822
What if I screwed up
the town's plan?

31:04.990 --> 31:07.701
Fuck! This fucker's gonna spread
like the plague, man!

31:07.826 --> 31:10.871
Kids are gonna start
falling asleep, it's gonna--

31:10.913 --> 31:12.289
Let's leave, man.
Let's leave right now.

31:12.372 --> 31:13.248
No, I can't leave.

31:13.290 --> 31:14.374
Why not?

31:14.458 --> 31:16.251
I gotta go talk to Lori.
I gotta see if she's OK.

31:16.251 --> 31:17.544
Well, is she worth dying for?

31:17.544 --> 31:20.047
Because if you fall asleep,
you ain't waking up.

31:20.047 --> 31:23.258
If that's the case,
how come you're not dead?

31:23.258 --> 31:24.426
Or any of the freaks at Westin?

31:24.426 --> 31:27.554
When's the last time
you even had a nightmare?

31:27.596 --> 31:29.014
I don't know.

31:29.056 --> 31:30.891
I can't remember
my dreams anymore.

31:32.392 --> 31:35.312
Look, just give me
one night, OK?

31:35.354 --> 31:38.148
Just let me find Lori,
and then we're out of here.

31:39.566 --> 31:41.443
I swear.

31:42.778 --> 31:43.695
All right.

31:43.779 --> 31:45.489
If your ass isn't back here by
dawn, I'm gone.

31:45.489 --> 31:48.492
We clear on that?

31:48.492 --> 31:52.162
This baby's my brother's
pride and joy, so be careful.

32:23.527 --> 32:24.528
Oh, shit.

32:24.528 --> 32:25.529
Linderman!

32:25.571 --> 32:28.448
Shack, I don't drink.

32:47.009 --> 32:50.429
Hi, Lori. Didn't think
I'd see you here.

32:50.429 --> 32:52.097
Can I get you
something to drink?

32:52.097 --> 32:55.601
Smooth opening, but, you know,
we're already taken care of.

32:55.601 --> 32:57.853
What happened
to your clothes?

32:57.853 --> 32:59.855
Oh, this.

32:59.980 --> 33:00.981
I was playing
a drinking game...

33:01.064 --> 33:04.276
with some
of the lower primates...

33:04.276 --> 33:05.736
and I guess I'm penalized
for my ability...

33:05.777 --> 33:07.321
to read above
a fourth-grade level.

33:07.362 --> 33:09.072
Linderman, you know,
I always pictured you...

33:09.072 --> 33:11.366
as a straight up bedwetter.

33:11.450 --> 33:13.368
You know what, Kia?

33:13.368 --> 33:14.828
I used to think you hated me...

33:14.828 --> 33:16.455
because you thought
I wasn't good enough for Lori...

33:16.455 --> 33:17.664
but that's not it.

33:17.748 --> 33:19.917
You tear me down
to make yourself feel better...

33:19.917 --> 33:21.251
because you really
hate yourself...

33:21.251 --> 33:22.961
which is kind of pathetic
when you actually...

33:22.961 --> 33:24.087
stop and think about it,
assuming, of course...

33:24.087 --> 33:25.923
you can think
with all that makeup...

33:25.923 --> 33:27.925
weighing down your head.

33:33.555 --> 33:35.516
The cops said Blake
committed suicide.

33:35.557 --> 33:37.017
Apparently,
it was grief over Trey.

33:37.100 --> 33:38.227
No, man, that's bullshit.

33:38.310 --> 33:40.229
I heard some guy Krueger
killed them both.

33:40.229 --> 33:42.189
Said his name to my parents,
they almost shit themselves.

33:42.189 --> 33:43.106
Yeah, yeah, yeah, man,
and I heard...

33:43.106 --> 33:44.525
that Freddy freak,
he used to live here.

33:44.525 --> 33:46.860
Fucking gutted Trey like
a Goddamn turkey, man.

33:46.902 --> 33:50.739
Like I heard his intestines and
shit was on the floor--

33:50.739 --> 33:53.826
Oh, shit. I'm sorry.

33:56.203 --> 33:58.288
Oh, my God.

33:58.288 --> 34:00.874
Look who's here.
Look who's here!

34:09.967 --> 34:11.885
What are you looking at?

34:11.969 --> 34:14.179
Come on, come on, let's dance.

34:14.179 --> 34:16.514
Come on, Linderman, let's go.

34:16.514 --> 34:18.433
Where have you been, Will?

34:18.516 --> 34:20.185
Didn't you get my letters?

34:20.185 --> 34:21.562
What letters?

34:21.562 --> 34:24.438
They must've never
even mailed them.

34:24.438 --> 34:27.317
Who?

34:27.317 --> 34:31.362
The...doctors at Westin Hills.

34:32.572 --> 34:35.659
I've been in
a psychiatric hospital.

34:35.659 --> 34:37.119
Mark was with me there.

34:37.119 --> 34:39.871
Some other kids, too.

34:39.871 --> 34:41.790
I don't understand.

34:44.042 --> 34:45.627
Well, I saw on the news
the other night...

34:45.627 --> 34:47.629
I mean, that kid that was
killed at your house.

34:47.670 --> 34:50.340
I mean, I needed to know
that you were safe.

34:50.424 --> 34:51.925
What happened?

34:51.925 --> 34:53.385
I don't know.
I don't know.

34:53.385 --> 34:55.179
Nobody knows.
Nobody saw what happened...

34:55.179 --> 34:56.638
and the police have been
acting really weird...

34:56.638 --> 34:58.056
Iike they know something...

34:58.056 --> 35:00.184
and I heard them
mention some name.

35:00.184 --> 35:01.810
Some...

35:01.935 --> 35:04.146
Freddy. Freddy Krueger.

35:04.146 --> 35:05.981
Where was your dad?

35:06.064 --> 35:07.316
Out of town.

35:07.441 --> 35:08.609
Are you sure?

35:08.734 --> 35:10.235
What is going on, Will?

35:10.319 --> 35:11.820
Well, look, four years ago,
I thought l--

35:11.945 --> 35:13.030
Enough with
this bullshit talk.

35:13.071 --> 35:15.032
Let's go shake our ass
on the dance floor.

35:15.032 --> 35:16.283
Come on!

35:33.967 --> 35:35.761
I'm dead one day...

35:35.761 --> 35:37.763
and you're already out
getting shit-faced?

35:37.763 --> 35:38.931
Same old Gibb!

35:38.972 --> 35:43.393
Trey, l--
I can't believe it.

35:43.477 --> 35:45.062
Come on, let's go.

35:47.064 --> 35:50.526
Babe, don't make me
ask you twice, OK?

35:52.110 --> 35:53.862
Now!

36:03.372 --> 36:05.249
Trey?

36:52.045 --> 36:53.797
No!

36:53.881 --> 36:55.632
Open the door!

36:55.716 --> 36:57.384
Please, the door--

37:39.801 --> 37:41.678
No! No!

38:03.826 --> 38:05.452
You're the one
that killed Trey!

38:05.452 --> 38:09.873
Oh, don't worry about
my little errand boy.

38:09.998 --> 38:14.461
The only to fear
is fear himself!

39:38.128 --> 39:40.380
No!

39:42.007 --> 39:43.509
She's mine.

39:43.550 --> 39:46.762
Mine! Mine!

39:53.393 --> 39:56.855
This everclear
is kicking my ass.

39:56.855 --> 39:57.898
This--

40:10.744 --> 40:13.205
Check out this fucking guy.

40:13.205 --> 40:14.414
Well, hey, Jethro!

40:14.414 --> 40:17.417
This is a rave,
not a Halloween party.

40:17.417 --> 40:21.171
Why don't you go
find yourself a pig to fuck?

40:21.171 --> 40:22.673
Yeah!

40:22.673 --> 40:25.968
Invite only, cornpoke,
and you weren't invite--

40:26.009 --> 40:28.011
Son of a bitch.

40:37.312 --> 40:38.689
Yeah!

40:38.814 --> 40:41.483
Burn, motherfucker!

40:59.418 --> 41:01.587
No!

41:28.614 --> 41:29.573
Run, man, run!

41:40.626 --> 41:43.545
Freak!
You killed my brother!

41:56.517 --> 41:58.727
Gibb! Oh, my God!

41:58.810 --> 42:00.562
Oh, Gibb! No!

42:00.562 --> 42:02.022
Let's go!
Let's go, come on!

42:08.403 --> 42:10.405
Was that him?

42:10.447 --> 42:12.574
The guy you were talking about--
Freddy Krueger.

42:12.658 --> 42:14.326
No, that wasn't
the guy in my dream.

42:14.326 --> 42:15.244
That was somebody else!

42:15.369 --> 42:18.163
Who cares about some
fucking dream guy, OK?

42:18.163 --> 42:19.915
That psycho
in the hockey mask was real.

42:19.998 --> 42:22.167
Dude, that goalie was
pissed about something.

42:22.209 --> 42:23.377
We need to find the police.

42:23.418 --> 42:25.546
No, no! Fuck the police!

42:25.671 --> 42:27.130
Just take me home, Will.

42:36.473 --> 42:38.767
Gibb, l--

42:38.851 --> 42:40.310
I can't believe she...

42:40.352 --> 42:41.395
I know.

42:45.816 --> 42:48.652
Look, call me later, OK?
Please.

42:48.652 --> 42:50.195
Just to check in.

42:56.785 --> 42:57.619
Bye, Will.

42:57.703 --> 42:59.997
Be careful.

43:18.182 --> 43:19.600
Will, I'm gonna go inside now.

43:19.600 --> 43:22.436
I think that's the last thing
you should do right now.

43:22.477 --> 43:24.188
Oh, Will, please.

43:24.188 --> 43:25.230
After everything
that's happened...

43:25.272 --> 43:26.148
I just want to go to--

43:26.273 --> 43:28.859
There's more
to it than that.

43:28.859 --> 43:32.279
Look, I tried to tell
you this earlier.

43:32.321 --> 43:33.822
The reason
I was sent to Westin...

43:33.822 --> 43:38.160
is because I saw
your dad kill your mom.

43:39.203 --> 43:41.663
Will, my mom died
in a car accident.

43:41.788 --> 43:43.957
No, that's what he
wanted you to believe...

43:44.082 --> 43:45.167
but I was there, Lori.

43:45.250 --> 43:48.378
I was sneaking up to your room,
like I used to do.

43:48.462 --> 43:50.172
Only you weren't there.

43:52.716 --> 43:55.010
I saw him kill her.

43:56.762 --> 43:57.679
Dad!

43:57.721 --> 43:59.014
Get out of the van.

43:59.139 --> 44:00.641
Get out of the van!
Where were you?

44:00.724 --> 44:01.558
What are you doing?

44:01.683 --> 44:03.018
I've been looking
all over for you!

44:03.018 --> 44:04.102
Get away from her!

44:04.102 --> 44:05.437
You're in a helluva
lot of trouble, you know that?

44:05.479 --> 44:07.022
Like I give
a shit anymore.

44:07.022 --> 44:08.232
Get in the house!

44:08.232 --> 44:09.441
You! I'm taking you
back to Westin.

44:09.483 --> 44:11.401
No! No way!
You can't trust him, Lori.

44:11.401 --> 44:13.070
Whatever you do,
don't go home with him!

44:13.153 --> 44:14.655
No, listen to me!

44:14.780 --> 44:16.615
He was the one
who had me committed!

44:16.657 --> 44:18.116
You didn't understand.

44:18.242 --> 44:19.576
You still don't.
You were confused!

44:19.618 --> 44:20.619
Stop it!

44:20.619 --> 44:22.120
Both of you, stop it!

44:22.162 --> 44:23.705
Damn it, Will!
I am not gonna let you...

44:23.705 --> 44:25.582
endanger my daughter again!

44:25.582 --> 44:27.709
Not after everything
that's happened!

44:27.793 --> 44:29.962
Stop it! Stop it! Fuck!

44:30.003 --> 44:32.256
Lori!

44:37.719 --> 44:40.264
I--l--

44:40.264 --> 44:42.140
Did Mom die
in a car accident?

44:42.182 --> 44:44.184
Yes. Of course she did.

44:44.268 --> 44:45.686
