44:45.686 --> 44:47.271
Show me a death certificate.

44:47.271 --> 44:49.523
Show me an autopsy report.

44:49.523 --> 44:52.067
Lori, I don't think now
is the right time--

44:52.067 --> 44:53.026
Really, Dad?

44:53.026 --> 44:54.736
Because I think
it's a perfect time!

44:54.820 --> 44:56.405
Why didn't you tell me
about Westin Hills?

44:56.405 --> 44:57.823
Do you work there?

44:57.823 --> 44:59.908
Because I thought you were
a fucking general practitioner!

45:00.033 --> 45:01.827
Yes, l...

45:01.910 --> 45:04.246
I do some consulting
there now, but...

45:04.329 --> 45:05.956
it's--it isn't
what you think.

45:05.956 --> 45:09.418
Oh, my God.

45:09.418 --> 45:12.212
So you knew about Will
this whole time.

45:12.212 --> 45:15.716
Lori, listen to me.

45:15.716 --> 45:19.720
You're upset.
We both are.

45:19.845 --> 45:21.722
Now I think what you need now...

45:21.722 --> 45:24.892
more than anything
is to get some rest.

45:24.933 --> 45:26.518
Why don't I give you
some pills...

45:26.518 --> 45:28.145
and that'll help you sleep...

45:28.228 --> 45:30.522
and then we talk
about it in the morning?

45:30.647 --> 45:32.357
I don't want
to sleep, Dad!

45:32.357 --> 45:34.359
I want to know why
you've been lying to me!

45:34.443 --> 45:35.486
We'll talk about it
in the morning!

45:35.486 --> 45:37.196
Now do what I say!

45:37.196 --> 45:38.530
Lori! Lori!

45:42.910 --> 45:45.078
Open this door.
Open this door!

45:45.162 --> 45:46.413
Go away!

45:46.413 --> 45:47.372
Damn it, Lori!

45:47.372 --> 45:48.999
<i>Let me in!</i>

45:54.838 --> 45:55.881
Goddamn it!

46:17.402 --> 46:19.780
It's OK, it's me.
It's me, shh! Shh!

46:19.780 --> 46:21.824
You OK? Are you OK?

46:21.949 --> 46:23.951
It's me, all right?

46:23.992 --> 46:28.622
I don't know how your father's
connected to all this...

46:28.622 --> 46:29.915
but I think
Mark was right.

46:29.915 --> 46:32.626
There's some kind of cover-up
going on here with Krueger.

46:34.545 --> 46:36.713
We can't trust the police.

46:38.340 --> 46:39.967
We can't trust
any of the adults.

46:42.219 --> 46:43.679
So what do we do?

46:43.679 --> 46:45.347
We gotta get to Mark.

46:45.597 --> 46:47.182
He's the expert in all of this.

46:47.182 --> 46:48.141
He'll know what's going on.

46:58.277 --> 47:02.781
You always looked out
for me, bro.

47:03.782 --> 47:06.034
