48:10.807 --> 48:12.684
Hey, Mark.

48:12.809 --> 48:14.228
You didn't forget
about me, did you?

48:14.311 --> 48:15.604
Oh, God.

48:15.646 --> 48:17.606
Oh, that's right!

48:17.648 --> 48:18.941
Everyone forgot!

48:18.941 --> 48:21.235
That's why they weren't
afraid anymore!

48:21.235 --> 48:22.778
