shut Jason back down.

53:02.224 --> 53:03.809
Wait a minute.

53:03.809 --> 53:06.687
Freddy died by fire,
Jason by water.

53:06.770 --> 53:08.772
How can we use that?

53:08.772 --> 53:11.483
I think we should
concentrate on Jason first.

53:11.483 --> 53:13.068
But I thought we decided...

53:13.152 --> 53:14.778
that Freddy was the one
pulling the strings.

53:14.820 --> 53:17.197
Shouldn't we go
after him first?

53:17.197 --> 53:19.700
