a sacrifice.

53:22.369 --> 53:23.787
Yeah, yeah, totally.

53:23.871 --> 53:26.915
Like a virgin, right?
Someone pure.

53:32.087 --> 53:34.423
Dude, don't look at me.

53:34.464 --> 53:36.800
Even if you pay for it,
it still counts.

53:36.800 --> 53:38.802
Oh, come on.

53:38.886 --> 53:41.513
Look, we all know who
the real virgin is here.

53:41.513 --> 53:44.057
-Kia!
-Oh, come on, Lori.

53:44.183 --> 53:45.934
