he can fuck somebody like me?

53:55.777 --> 53:57.279
Let's tie the bitch up.

54:00.157 --> 54:02.075
What?

54:04.369 --> 54:06.705
Don't worry, angel.

54:06.705 --> 54:08.332
You've still got me.

54:08.373 --> 54:10.709
Come on, give daddy a kiss.

54:15.172 --> 54:18.675
Your eyes say no-no...

54:18.759 --> 54:23.055
but my mouth says yes-yes.

54:27.226 --> 54:28.811
Lori, are you all right?

54:28.811 --> 54:30.020
You fell asleep.

54:37.778 --> 54:39.780
Oh, shit!

54:43.492 --> 54:45.369
I pulled that out of my dream.

54:45.494 --> 54:47.371
How is that possible?

54:47.371 --> 54:49.331
Anything is possible now!

54:49.373 --> 54:50.582
God, you just don't get it!

54:50.582 --> 54:52.668
Oh, God, y'all, two killers?

54:52.709 --> 54:54.461
We're not safe awake or asleep.

54:54.586 --> 54:56.338
It's not the sleep
that's killing us...

54:56.338 --> 54:57.256
it's our dreams.

54:57.256 --> 54:59.883
At Westin, Mark and l
never had dreams.

54:59.883 --> 55:02.469
Were you on any drugs?

55:02.594 --> 55:04.888
Yeah, but there's
something called hypnocil.

55:04.888 --> 55:06.890
