55:13.438 --> 55:14.857
not even approved yet
by the F.D.A.

55:14.982 --> 55:16.733
Oh, shit.

55:16.733 --> 55:20.487
Used for...
suppression of dreams.

55:20.487 --> 55:23.824
We need those pills,
enough for all of us.

55:23.907 --> 55:25.909
Can you get us
back to Westin Hills?

55:45.429 --> 55:46.930
All right,
this isn't it, guys.

55:47.014 --> 55:48.765
Come on, let's go.

55:48.765 --> 55:49.725
Hey, dude.

55:49.725 --> 55:51.018
Let's take a little
J-break, huh?

55:51.018 --> 55:53.562
