57:21.191 --> 57:23.485
Cool...yeah.

57:33.078 --> 57:35.539
What the fuck?

57:48.844 --> 57:50.179
Nice.

57:57.561 --> 57:59.188
Oh, yeah.

58:03.525 --> 58:05.152
Hold up, man.

58:16.705 --> 58:17.706
What?

58:23.462 --> 58:24.546
