01:00:05.939 --> 01:00:06.857
We gotta keep looking.

01:00:06.940 --> 01:00:08.192
Maybe there's some down here.

01:00:08.317 --> 01:00:10.194
Damn, it's gotta
be here somewhere.

01:00:20.370 --> 01:00:21.497
Freeburg, come on!

01:00:21.497 --> 01:00:23.290
Come on! Come on!

01:00:23.290 --> 01:00:25.459
What are you waiting for?
Come on!

01:00:25.459 --> 01:00:27.544
Freeburg, time to go.

01:00:27.544 --> 01:00:29.796
We gotta go!
Now! come on!

01:00:29.796 --> 01:00:32.341
Let me handle this, bitch.

01:00:32.341 --> 01:00:33.967
What?

01:00:35.469 --> 01:00:37.137
Come on, come on!
OK, let's go!

01:00:38.514 --> 01:00:39.806
Let's go.

01:00:39.848 --> 01:00:40.891
No, wait, wait!

01:00:41.016 --> 01:00:41.934
Look.

01:00:45.437 --> 01:00:46.897
Come to Freddy.

01:00:48.023 --> 01:00:50.818
These are my children, Jason.

01:00:51.193 --> 01:00:53.487
Go back where you belong!

01:01:03.747 --> 01:01:05.916
Fuck you!

01:01:07.626 --> 01:01:09.461
Linderman...

01:01:11.255 --> 01:01:14.466
<i>These are my children, Jason.</i>

01:01:14.550 --> 01:01:16.844
<i>Go back where you belong.</i>

01:01:28.689 --> 01:01:32.359
<i>Jason...Jason.</i>

01:01:32.442 --> 01:01:35.654
<i>My special, special boy.</i>

01:01:39.825 --> 01:01:42.077
I'm disappointed
in you, Jason.

01:01:42.077 --> 01:01:43.954
You disobeyed me.

01:01:43.954 --> 01:01:45.539
You were supposed
to come back home...

01:01:45.664 --> 01:01:47.291
just kill a few of them!

01:01:47.416 --> 01:01:49.418
But I blame myself.
I should've known...

01:01:49.459 --> 01:01:51.545
you wouldn't be able
to stop killing!

01:01:51.670 --> 01:01:56.508
You are like a big, stupid dog
who can't stop eating...

01:01:56.592 --> 01:02:00.804
even though your master
said you've had enough!

01:02:06.643 --> 01:02:10.898
Now it's time to put
this bad dog to sleep...

01:02:13.192 --> 01:02:14.318
for good!

01:02:21.200 --> 01:02:22.701
Not my arm!

01:02:47.810 --> 01:02:50.145
Welcome to my nightmare.

01:03:09.414 --> 01:03:11.583
Penny for your thoughts, chief!

01:03:13.335 --> 01:03:15.420
Oh, scary.

01:03:34.523 --> 01:03:35.732
Tilt.

01:03:58.422 --> 01:04:00.465
Why won't you die?

01:04:25.073 --> 01:04:27.075
Come on. Come on!

01:04:44.384 --> 01:04:47.763
So you are afraid of something
after all, huh?

01:04:57.731 --> 01:05:00.275
How in the fuck did I let y'all
talk me into this?

01:05:00.275 --> 01:05:02.277
Why don't we just
try and do it here?

01:05:02.319 --> 01:05:04.196
Why go all the way
to Crystal Lake?

01:05:04.279 --> 01:05:06.281
Best-case scenario: Jason wins.

01:05:06.323 --> 01:05:08.867
He'll already be home,
back where he belongs.

01:05:08.992 --> 01:05:10.160
I mean, why follow us anymore?

01:05:10.160 --> 01:05:11.787
And if Freddy wins?

01:05:11.787 --> 01:05:14.623
At least Jason
has home-field advantage.

01:05:38.772 --> 01:05:41.984
Aww...how sweet.

01:05:43.068 --> 01:05:45.195
You ugly little shit.

01:05:45.195 --> 01:05:49.825
Now there's a face...
only a mother could love!

01:05:52.035 --> 01:05:53.245
Yeah!

01:05:53.245 --> 01:05:55.080
Now we're getting somewhere.

01:05:55.080 --> 01:05:57.624
Let's see
what really scares you.

01:06:04.423 --> 01:06:07.176
And dig a little deeper.

01:06:35.621 --> 01:06:39.917
<i>I'm dying to see what skeletons
are hidden in your closet.</i>

01:06:55.974 --> 01:06:58.227
We're seriously running
out of tranq here, guys.

01:06:58.227 --> 01:07:01.438
I got maybe one dose,
plus enough for Lori.

01:07:01.438 --> 01:07:02.648
Well, we're almost there.

01:07:02.648 --> 01:07:03.982
Then I better get going.

01:07:03.982 --> 01:07:05.192
No, no, just...

01:07:10.072 --> 01:07:11.323
I don't want you to go.

01:07:11.323 --> 01:07:12.783
I'm coming back.

01:07:12.825 --> 01:07:15.452
Just give me fifteen minutes,
then wake me up.

01:07:15.494 --> 01:07:17.579
I'll bring that bastard
Freddy back through.

01:07:17.621 --> 01:07:20.290
