01:07:48.443 --> 01:07:52.489
Freak show! Freak show!
Freak show! Freak show!

01:07:52.573 --> 01:07:53.949
Bull's-eye!

01:07:57.953 --> 01:07:59.830
Freak show!
Freak show! Freak show!

01:07:59.955 --> 01:08:01.206
Try this on!

01:08:02.374 --> 01:08:05.377
Freak show!
Freak show! Freak show!

01:08:09.131 --> 01:08:10.507
Stupid!

01:08:13.677 --> 01:08:15.596
