01:08:15.596 --> 01:08:17.973
Can't you see I'm busy here?

01:08:18.098 --> 01:08:19.433
You mean you're not coming?

01:08:22.227 --> 01:08:25.354
It's not my fault this bitch
is dead on her feet.

01:08:33.863 --> 01:08:35.323
It's been five minutes.

01:08:35.448 --> 01:08:37.493
Well, that was the last
of the tranq, OK? We're out.

01:08:37.493 --> 01:08:39.328
Calm down, OK?
Just relax!

01:08:52.591 --> 01:08:54.426
Heeeeelp!

01:08:54.551 --> 01:08:57.930
Wait! Give me your hand!

01:08:58.055 --> 01:09:00.682
Give me your hand!

01:09:02.100 --> 01:09:03.143
Help!

01:09:03.227 --> 01:09:05.395
Jason?

01:09:05.395 --> 01:09:07.104
Jason Vorhees?

01:09:17.282 --> 01:09:19.243
Y'all...y'all...

01:09:19.243 --> 01:09:20.202
Y'all, something's wrong.

01:09:20.243 --> 01:09:21.453
